Package: visPed
Title: Visualizes Pedigrees
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Gavin", "Lee", email = "lee.gavin.k@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut")),
        person("Qing", "Zhang", role = "aut"))
Description: This package is a short script which can be interpreted as
    a fork of the kinship2 package where additional affection statuses
    can be shown in the context of cancer syndromes. It also contains a
    feature to convert compatible data frames into visNetwork plots specifically
    for pedigrees with disease affliction.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
  kinship2,
  rlang,
  RColorBrewer,
  visNetwork
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
